# The embedded SPA is a generated artifact (built from tools/runstatus), staged
# by `node esbuild.mjs` (or `make build`) — never committed. Mirrors how
# internal/runstatus/web/assets gitignores the built index.html. Only the
# .gitkeep placeholder is tracked so webview.ts's media root always exists.
